ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v28.group

Class PPP_PCB_PROBLEM

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractStructure
      • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractGroup
        • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v28.group.PPP_PCB_PROBLEM
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Group, Structure, Visitable, Serializable

    public class PPP_PCB_PROBLEM
extends AbstractGroup

    Represents a PPP_PCB_PROBLEM group structure (a Group object). A Group is an ordered collection of message segments that can repeat together or be optionally in/excluded together. This Group contains the following elements:

    • 1: PRB (Problem Details)
    • 2: NTE (Notes and Comments) optional repeating
    • 3: VAR (Variance) optional repeating
    • 4: PPP_PCB_PROBLEM_ROLE (a Group object) optional repeating
    • 5: PPP_PCB_PROBLEM_OBSERVATION (a Group object) optional repeating
    • 6: PPP_PCB_GOAL (a Group object) optional repeating
    • 7: PPP_PCB_ORDER (a Group object) optional repeating
    See Also:
